  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unleash the Future: Robo Tennis </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dive into the fast-paced world of Robo Tennis!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against elite robots from top constructors in adrenaline-pumping tournaments. Earn credits, unlock advanced tech, and build the ultimate robot athlete. Customize your robot’s attributes for peak performance and dominate the pitch!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/f2c8cb416cbf80e2f18b556adb9925f6.poster.avif?t=1749842403\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/f2c8cb416cbf80e2f18b556adb9925f6.webm?t=1749842403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/f2c8cb416cbf80e2f18b556adb9925f6.mp4?t=1749842403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock New Technologies</strong>: Spend your winnings on cutting-edge parts, upgrades, and special shots to enhance your robot’s abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build Your Ultimate Robot</strong>: Choose from a variety of components and special shots at your factory HQ to assemble a winning machine.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Secure Sponsorships</strong>: Win matches to attract sponsors, earn cash, and deck out your robot in their colors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Acquire Trophies</strong>: Prove your prowess by winning major tournaments and earning trophies for your office. But beware—losing big games means losing those precious trophies!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the revolution and become the ultimate robo-champion! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/68436aa99790705baba8395883b44450.poster.avif?t=1749842403\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/68436aa99790705baba8395883b44450.webm?t=1749842403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/68436aa99790705baba8395883b44450.mp4?t=1749842403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unleash the Future: Robo Tennis </strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dive into the fast-paced world of Robo Tennis!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against elite robots from top constructors in adrenaline-pumping tournaments. Earn credits, unlock advanced tech, and build the ultimate robot athlete. Customize your robot’s attributes for peak performance and dominate the pitch!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/f2c8cb416cbf80e2f18b556adb9925f6.poster.avif?t=1749842403\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/f2c8cb416cbf80e2f18b556adb9925f6.webm?t=1749842403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/f2c8cb416cbf80e2f18b556adb9925f6.mp4?t=1749842403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock New Technologies</strong>: Spend your winnings on cutting-edge parts, upgrades, and special shots to enhance your robot’s abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build Your Ultimate Robot</strong>: Choose from a variety of components and special shots at your factory HQ to assemble a winning machine.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Secure Sponsorships</strong>: Win matches to attract sponsors, earn cash, and deck out your robot in their colors.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Acquire Trophies</strong>: Prove your prowess by winning major tournaments and earning trophies for your office. But beware—losing big games means losing those precious trophies!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the revolution and become the ultimate robo-champion! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/68436aa99790705baba8395883b44450.poster.avif?t=1749842403\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/68436aa99790705baba8395883b44450.webm?t=1749842403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3322930/extras/68436aa99790705baba8395883b44450.mp4?t=1749842403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
